en_187441_0	Four persons from the same family died following an accident involving a three-wheeler and a lorry at Yatigalpotta, Galewela.
en_187441_1	Police said that the head-on collision took place this morning (Apr. 02).
en_187441_2	The victims, father, mother, son and daughter of the same family.
en_187441_3	They were residents of Attanagalle.
en_187441_4	Father was aged 46 and the mother was 42-years-old.
en_187441_5	The son was aged 20 and his sister was aged 8.
